reviewText: this video has a nice flow to it, and has excellent progression with linking the parts together as you go along...you also get a cd with the music used in the video

This dvd is excellent. It is slow paced and easy to follow. They go over the different steps many times which is a big plus for someone just starting out in learning hip hop. I highly recommend it.

  Cheryl Frey
Great if you want to learn freestyle dance moves to use in the club, not a choreographed dance routine. Will help you better understand how to dance. Audio quality is poor.
